data.title: Final Fantasy
data.meta_description: List Games.txt - Free download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read online for free. The document lists the titles of over 500 PC games stored on individual disks. The genres include racing, simulation, strategy, RPG, action, adventure, mini games and more. Many of the titles are for classic franchises like Age of Empires, Assassin's Creed, Civilization, and Tropico. The document provides a catalog of the game collection but does not describe the content or quality of any individual title.
